# 🛰️ Real-Time Location-Based Alert System

This web-based system uses geolocation to track the user's live position and alert them upon entering predefined unsafe zones.

## 💡 Features
- Real-time tracking using browser geolocation API
- Geofencing with multiple unsafe zone detection
- Easy to customize alert zones
- Minimalistic design for demonstration

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript (No frameworks)

## 🚀 How to Run
1. Download or clone this repository.
2. Open `index.html` in a browser.
3. Allow location access and see alerts based on your location.
